title: Week 2 NFL DFS Picks & Advice (Football 9/17)
description:
Will Brinson and Heath Cummings are back for another week of NFL DFS advice. The guys break down the entire Sunday slate, so let's get into it!
Falcons-Cowboys (5:40)
Bucs-Panthers (9:20)
Lions-Packers (13:40)
Vikings-Colts (16:10)
Eagles-Rams (22:30)
49ers-Jets (25:30)
Bears-Giants (29:05)
Bills-Dolphins (33:45)
Broncos-Steelers (34:45)
Jags-Titans (36:15)
Ravens-Texans (38:45)
Chiefs-Chargers (44:15)
Washington-Arizona (47:15)
Patriots-Seahawks (50:15)
